column2: ALPHA BLACK TO PAPA BEAR. ALL RUSSIANS ARE NEUTRALIZED. OVER.
ALPHA TO BRAVO. WE ARE DONE HERE. COME TO PICK US UP. OVER.
OKAY HERE WE GO ALPHA. GET READY FOR INSERTION, LANDING ZONE IN SIGHT. OVER.
GOOD LUCK. GO BACK ME SOME RUSSIANS. BRAVO OUT.
BRAVO TO ALPHA. GET READY FOR EXTRACTION. OVER.
PAPA BEAR TO ALPHA. ROGER. RETURN TO BASE. OVER.
PAPA BEAR TO ALPHA BLACK. WELCOME BACK. OVER.
